title: Modern 2+2 in Mid Wilshire-Rooftop Garden Terrace + Panoramic Views
posting_body: ['Windsor Square Villas', '850 Crenshaw Boulevard Los Angeles, CA 90005', 'show contact info', 'Features in this apartment home:', '– Stainless-steel dishwasher, oven, microwave drawer, and range hood', '– High-gloss Italian cabinets', '– Spacious gourmet-designed kitchen', '– Built-in spacious walk-in closets with sleek bi-pass sliding doors', '– In-house networking', '– Modern-custom designed tile', '– In-unit washer and dryer', '– Hardwood flooring throughout', '– Contemporary designer vanity lights in bathrooms', 'Amenities at our property:', '– Entertaining rooftop & outdoor BBQ with dining area', '– Intercom systems', '– Pre-wired for Time Warner Cable, high-speed broadband, in-house networking, security, CAT5 telephone & RG6 TV', '– Rooftop garden terrace with panoramic views', '– 2 reserved parking spaces for each unit', '– Modern-design lobby', '– Wi-Fi available throughout', '– Well-maintained entertainment garden', '– Electric Car Charging by – ChargePoint', 'Pet policy at our property:', 'Cats and Dogs Welcome.', 'Additional Fees and Deposit May Apply.', 'Call for Details and Restrictions.', 'About the community:', 'Welcome to Windsor Square Villas.', 'Brand new, modern, luxurious apartments, in the desirable and prestigious neighborhood of Windsor Square.', 'Our community offers a contemporary, robust, and dynamically different lifestyle that is new and exciting, featuring elegant architecture, top of the line stainless-steel appliances, in-unit washer and dryer, spacious private balconies, designer fixtures and hardwood flooring.', 'Complemented with sweeping panoramic views of downtown, the Windsor Square Villas offer unparalleled modern design and functionality for you to live and to enjoy.', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Square Footage Is Approximate.', 'Prices subject to change without notice and units based on availability']
